## Power Saving Management

Go to _Settings â†’ Battery Lab â†’ Battery Saving Settings â†’ Disable **Power Saving Management For Apps**_

## Allow app to run in the background

Go to _Phone Master â†’ Toolbox â†’ Auto-start management â†’ **Allow app to run in background**_

## Lock the app in the Recent apps

Head to recent apps with the navigation bar or using gestures press the down arrow on the top of microg.

Press the first option with the ðŸ”’ icon.

